Pencheff Community Edition
==========================

Copyright 2026 Bala Sriharsha

This product is released under the Apache License, Version 2.0
(see ``LICENSE``).

This product invokes a number of third-party security tools as
subprocesses and ingests data from a number of public vulnerability
feeds. None of those tools' source code is bundled or statically
linked. Per-component licenses, sources, and redistribution posture
are documented in:

* ``THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md`` — root: Python deps, hosted services, the
  optional toolchain image, and the SAST scanner pack.
* ``plugins/pencheff/THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md`` — MCP plugin: external
  binary tools invoked by the orchestrator.

